# Agentic Architectures Knowledge Base

This project has a local RAG index built from `kb/` (Packt book on multi-agent systems).

## When to use

When the user asks about agentic patterns, chapters, maturity models, RAG, LLMOps, ADK, CrewAI, LangGraph, or book content — search the KB first.

## How to query (terminal)

```bash
python3 scripts/rag_query.py "your question here"
python3 scripts/rag_query.py "question" --chapter 5
python3 scripts/rag_query.py "question" --search-only
```

## Index location

- Vector store: `.rag/chroma/`
- Rebuild after KB changes: `python3 scripts/build_rag_index.py`
- Requires `OPENAI_API_KEY` in `.env`

Ground answers in retrieved sources. Cite chapter/section when possible.
